Title: Solutions of n-simplex Equation from Solutions of Braid Group

RepresentationAuthors: You-Quan Li and Zhan-Ning Hu

Comments: 8 pages, latex. The figures can be get from the authors

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A28 (1995) L219-L224

It is shown that a kind of solutions of n-simplex equation can be obtainedfrom representations of braid group. The symmetries in its solution space arealso discussed.